This is a Play 2.0 application template
=======================================

Important: Works only with Play 2.0.2 right now!
Intention is to provide a template for a Play 2! application. It should provide examplary code and technologies to
setup a new application quickly. This includes but is not limited to:

+ Scalate(Scaml) integration
+ bootstrap integration via LESS
+ differentiat between mobile and desktop clients
+ persistence in mongo
+ enabled to deploy to heroku
+ basic auth with facebook